"location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"","body_zh_TW":"","body_cs":"","body_da":"","body_nl":"","body_fi":"","body_fr":"","body_de":"","body_el":"","body_he":"","body_it":"","body_ja":"","body_ko":"","body_ms":"","body_no":"","body_pl":"","body_pt":"","body_es":"","body_sv":"","body_th":"","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"Everything as described, it can fit my jewelry easily for the travel. Highly recommended.","rating":"5","review_date":"10/11/2019 0:00","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Tre Mills","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"portable-jewelry-organizer-jewelry-storage-box-case-ideal-for-storing-your-earnings-rings-and-necklaces","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Uf9c6dccf26e2458d8156ae57a509fd34v.jpg, https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/U464fe5d88d7b49f68d3d3d10d0a87e73t.jpg, https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Uc2aac3ea6e1f4fb2ae0e13f81a7b4e67T.jpg","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"كل شيء كما هو موصوف، ويمكنني وضع مجوهراتي بسهولة أثناء السفر. أنصح به بشدة.","body_zh_TW":"一切都如描述的那樣，它能輕鬆裝下我旅行時需要攜帶的珠寶。強烈推薦。","body_cs":"Všechno dle popisu, šperky se mi snadno vejdou na cesty. Vřele doporučuji.","body_da":"Alt som beskrevet, det passer nemt til mine smykker på rejsen. Kan varmt anbefales.","body_nl":"Alles zoals beschreven, mijn sieraden passen er gemakkelijk in voor op reis. Een echte aanrader.","body_fi":"Kaikki kuvauksen mukaisesti, koruni sopivat tähän helposti matkalle. Suosittelen lämpimästi.","body_fr":"Conforme à la description, il est parfait pour ranger mes bijoux en voyage. Je le recommande vivement.","body_de":"Alles wie beschrieben, es bietet ausreichend Platz für meinen Schmuck auf Reisen. Sehr empfehlenswert.","body_el":"Όλα όπως περιγράφονται, χωράει εύκολα τα κοσμήματά μου για ταξίδια. Το συνιστώ ανεπιφύλακτα.","body_he":"הכל כמתואר, זה יכול להתאים בקלות לתכשיטים שלי לנסיעות. מומלץ מאוד.","body_it":"Tutto come descritto, può contenere facilmente i miei gioielli, il che è perfetto per i viaggi. Altamente consigliato.","body_ja":"説明通りの商品で、旅行用のジュエリーも楽に収納できます。非常におすすめです。","body_ko":"설명대로 모든 것이 완벽하고, 여행 중에 제 액세서리를 넣기에 딱 좋아요. 강력 추천합니다.","body_ms":"Semuanya seperti yang diterangkan, ia sesuai dengan barang kemas saya untuk perjalanan. Amat disyorkan.","body_no":"Alt som beskrevet, den får enkelt plass til smykkene mine på reisen. Anbefales på det sterkeste.","body_pl":"Wszystko zgodne z opisem, bez problemu zmieści się tam moja biżuteria w podróży. Gorąco polecam.","body_pt":"Tudo conforme descrito, cabe perfeitamente minhas joias para viagem. Recomendo muito.","body_es":"Todo tal como se describe, mis joyas caben perfectamente para viajar. Muy recomendable.","body_sv":"Allt enligt beskrivning, mina smycken får lätt plats på resan. Rekommenderas starkt.","body_th":"ทุกอย่างตรงตามคำอธิบาย ใส่เครื่องประดับของฉันได้สะดวกสำหรับการเดินทาง แนะนำเป็นอย่างยิ่ง","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"Very easy to use","rating":"5","review_date":"10/10/2019 0:00","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Aidan Wyman","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"portable-jewelry-organizer-jewelry-storage-box-case-ideal-for-storing-your-earnings-rings-and-necklaces","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"سهل الاستخدام للغاية","body_zh_TW":"非常易於使用","body_cs":"Velmi snadné použití","body_da":"Meget nem at bruge","body_nl":"Zeer eenvoudig in gebruik.","body_fi":"Erittäin helppokäyttöinen","body_fr":"Très facile à utiliser","body_de":"Sehr einfach zu bedienen","body_el":"Πολύ εύκολο στη χρήση","body_he":"קל מאוד לשימוש","body_it":"Molto facile da usare","body_ja":"非常に使いやすい","body_ko":"사용하기 매우 쉽습니다","body_ms":"Sangat mudah digunakan","body_no":"Veldig enkel å bruke","body_pl":"Bardzo łatwy w użyciu","body_pt":"Muito fácil de usar.","body_es":"Muy fácil de usar","body_sv":"Mycket lätt att använda","body_th":"ใช้